choices.text:
,

I'm sorry to hear that you're feeling down. It sounds like you're going through a tough time right now and it's understandable that you're feeling overwhelmed. It's important to remember that it's okay to feel this way and that it's normal to have ups and downs. It's also important to remember that you don't have to go through this alone. Is there someone you can talk to about how you're feeling? It could be a friend, family member, or even a professional. Talking to someone can help you to feel better and can help you to find ways to cope with your feelings.
